 PIN MAPPING - TASK A
Component	ESP32 Pin	Purpose
Button 1	GPIO 14	Mode Cycle Button
Button 2	GPIO 27	Reset Button
LED 1	GPIO 5	Red LED
LED 2	GPIO 18	Green LED
LED 3	GPIO 19	Blue LED (PWM Fade)
Buzzer	GPIO 25	Buzzer/Speaker
OLED SDA	GPIO 21	I2C Data (Default)
OLED SCL	GPIO 22	I2C Clock (Default)
All GND	GND	Ground
